<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Include Static Files
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    3. Add static file references in your app host file. The Material provider stylesheet loads its packaged Material Symbols fonts from <Code>_content/Blazorise.Material/fonts/</Code>. The Google Material Icons stylesheet is needed only when you use <Code>Blazorise.Icons.Material</Code>.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    <DocsPageUnorderedList>
        <DocsPageUnorderedListItem>
